<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> ciṟukaṭṭaināṭu maṉṟupoḻil kuḻi Ainūṟu maṟuppūr kuḻi muṉṉūṟu kacu<unclear>mu</unclear>r kuḻi Aiññūṟu kanuppūr kuḻi Āyiram kuṭicceṟu kuḻi muṉṉūṟu ciṟakkaḷappūṇṭi kuḻi Irunūṟum Iviṉūr kuḻi muṉṉūṟu Oṭṭappūṇṭi kuḻi Aiññūṟu 
<lb n="2"/>miṟutti Āttak<unclear>kū</unclear>r kuḻi muṉṉūṟu kuruttalūr kuḻi Aiññūṟu Ūṭṭakakūr kuḻi muṉṉūṟṟaimpatu kommalappūṇṭi kuḻi Irunūṟu vintūr kuḻi nāṉūṟu poṉṉalakkūr kuḻi Irunūṟu piṭiyūr <supplied reason="omitted">kuḻi</supplied> muṉṉūṟu
<lb n="3"/>cāteyaṉkoṇṭur kuḻi Irunūṟu virutaṅkapo<unclear>ṉṉa</unclear>l kuḻi muṉṉūṟu comeyaṉpūṇṭi kuḻi Irunūṟu pāṟcelmai kuḻi <unclear>nū</unclear>ṟṟaimpatu mutukoṭu kuḻi nūṟu vemur kuḻi muṉṉūṟu mulukkaltāvaṉpūṇṭi kuḻi nūṟu <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied>
</p>

